{"type":"message","id":"256d0895","parentId":"8ae41bfd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:14:14.488Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:af6a6a57-8b20-481c-a0d9-de27076df635 人体修复能力思考推送] 请研究并分享一个关于人类身体修复能力的前沿发现或有趣角度（如牙齿再生、器官自愈、细胞修复、组织工程等）。要求：1) 基于真实科学研究 2) 简短有趣 3) 包含一个令人惊叹的事实或进展。发送到微信：510723047。输出格式：【人体修复日报】+ 日期 + 主题 + 内容 + 来源/研究方向。\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 10:14 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 02:14 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774318454487}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfcbbaed","parentId":"256d0895","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:14:19.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我研究人类身体修复能力的前沿发现，并发送到微信。我需要：\n1. 先搜索相关科学研究\n2. 整理成要求的格式\n3. 注意：我无法直接发送到微信，需要说明这一点\n\n让我先搜索最新的人体修复能力研究。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_542c82af84524ac9abc02ef9","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"human body regeneration teeth organ self-healing 2025 2026 scientific breakthrough","count":8,"freshness":"year"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774318454488}}
