{"type":"message","id":"f11e3be3","parentId":"96ae3f83","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:14:26.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"web_search 需要 API key。让我尝试用 web_fetch 获取一些已知的研究页面，或者我可以用已有的知识来创建这个内容。\n\n实际上，我应该用已有的知识来创建这个推送内容，因为：\n1. web_search 需要 API key\n2. 这是一个 cron 定时任务，需要快速完成\n3. 我有很多关于人体修复能力的科学知识\n\n让我创建一个有趣且基于真实研究的内容。我知道一些前沿研究：\n- 牙齿再生：2025 年日本批准了牙齿再生药物临床试验\n- 器官自愈：肝脏再生能力\n- 细胞修复：端粒酶、干细胞\n- 组织工程：3D 生物打印器官\n\n让我创建一个引人入胜的推送。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f8cf1dbeb2f2493a8d30af03","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"tooth regeneration drug Japan 2025 clinical trial stem cells","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774318459341}}
